</ol><p><strong>ASPE STUDY OBSERVATION</strong>: The multiple child care systems  		are in the process of "gearing up" for managing the Pediatric HIV/ARC/AIDS  		problem. The desire to maintain family structure and to utilize extended family  		members, especially grandmothers, is the focus of social service activity.</p>
